Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.32,0:08:06.77,Style02,,0,0,0,,{\frz7\pos(385,281)}的詩集
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,茉莉的詩集
